#. <section class="sutta" id="an9.10"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an9.10:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 9"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 9"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an9.10:0.2"
msgid "1. Sambodhivagga"
msgstr "1. Awakening"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 10. Āhuneyyasutta → āhuneyyapuggalasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an9.10:0.3"
msgid "10. Āhuneyyasutta"
msgstr "10. Worthy of Offerings Dedicated to the Gods"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.373"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an9.10:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Navayime, bhikkhave, puggalā āhuneyyā pāhuneyyā dakkhiṇeyyā añjalikaraṇīyā "
"anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ lokassa."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, these nine people are worthy of offerings dedicated to the "
"gods, worthy of hospitality, worthy of a teacher’s offering, worthy of "
"greeting with joined palms, and are the supreme field of merit for the world."

msgctxt "an9.10:1.2"
msgid "Katame nava?"
msgstr "What nine?"

msgctxt "an9.10:1.3"
msgid ""
"Arahā, arahattāya paṭipanno, anāgāmī, anāgāmiphalasacchikiriyāya paṭipanno, "
"sakadāgāmī, sakadāgāmiphalasacchikiriyāya paṭipanno, sotāpanno, "
"sotāpattiphalasacchikiriyāya paṭipanno, gotrabhū—"
msgstr ""
"The perfected one, and the one practicing for perfection. The non-returner "
"and the one practicing to realize the fruit of non-return. The once-returner "
"and the one practicing to realize the fruit of once-return. The stream-"
"enterer and the one practicing to realize the fruit of stream-entry. And a "
"member of the spiritual family."

msgctxt "an9.10:1.4"
msgid ""
"ime kho, bhikkhave, nava puggalā āhuneyyā … pe … anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ "
"lokassā”ti."
msgstr ""
"These are the nine people who are worthy of offerings dedicated to the gods, "
"worthy of hospitality, worthy of a teacher’s offering, worthy of greeting "
"with joined palms, and are the supreme field of merit for the world.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.10:1.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.10:1.6"
msgid "Sambodhivaggo paṭhamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an9.10:2.1"
msgid "Sambodhi nissayo ceva,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an9.10:2.2"
msgid "Meghiya nandakaṃ balaṃ;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an9.10:2.3"
msgid "Sevanā sutavā sajjho,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an9.10:2.4"
msgid "Puggalo āhuneyyena cāti."
msgstr ""
